data.description: If you are looking for quality, this is it!  Largest and most solid bilding in the area -- Solid Brick -- no siding on this one!  No known repairs needed and never any water in the basement! Gorgeous Vintage features as marble walls and Mosaic tile in entry, solid wood beams and trims, etc. and YES, there is hardwood under all carpet on each floor.  Priced to sell -- Extremely rare -- all 3 bedroom units completed with gut rehab from roof to basement.  Building bumps out on both sides for exceptional square footage.  Great monthly income with room to grow.  All long terms tenants and all rent paid on time. Building completely runs itself as tenants take care of all cleaning, landscaping, garbage, snow removal and minor repairs.  Features:  tall wood beam ceilings, decorative fireplaces with built-in shelving.  NEW MECHANICALS- PLUMBING, ELECTRICAL, DRYWALL, BOILER, ENERGY EFFICIENT FURNACE, WINDOWS, KITCHENS & BATHS, NEW WATER HEATER and NEW ROOF.  Basement remodeled, waterproofed and New Sump Pump added!  LAUNDRY IN BASEMENT, GATED PARKING, NEWER PORCH, SOLD AS-IS, SUPER HOT AREA!! 4 NEW CONSTRUCTION HOMES ON THIS BLOCK ALONE! TRAIN AND HWY 2 BLOCKS AWAY. DOWNTOWN ONLY MINUTES DRIVE AWAY! NO VIOLATIONS. ALL LONG TERM TENANTS TAKE GOOD CARE OF BUILDING & PAY RENT ON TIME. BUILDING ORIGINALLY BUILD WITH 4 PHYSICAL UNITS ON PROPERTY BUT ZONING CERT IS FOR A 3 UNIT. GARDEN UNIT MAY BE POTENTIALLY USED AS IN-LAW/OWNER UNIT, DUPLEX WITH FIRST FLOOR OR CONVERTED TO LEGAL CITY ADDITIONAL DWELLING UNIT, CHECK ELIGIBILITY. OWNER DOES NOT GUARANTEE LEGALITY OF GARDEN UNIT.  DON'T MISS THIS OPPORTUNITY IN THIS BOOMING AREA!!
